{"type": "article", "id": 13895, "title": "户外烤三明治机", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-24T08:03:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000247LS0lVIe4p7O1hR8t.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t户外运动品牌 Poler 最近推出了一款便利烤三明治机，方便用户在户外烤三明治，火腿等食物，只需要把食材放进模具里面，然后放置在火上烤，便可以轻松制作健康的三明治，为户外活动中食物的制作提供了便利。目前售价 53 美元，<a href=\"http://www.polerstuff.com/products/the-poler-sandwich-maker?variant=3815163588\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141543EycbSAvsRNloi2Zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141543cfD3hJ4HRWCunQyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141544nqNzLUhM8kpBAwIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56445312\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141544l7X51duopEZMSTFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141545TCG7yrY8inHuzFow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141545Kmn1UN9MHqZODryg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141546qN3SrgAjl8d2wDhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}